messages.message:
I shared this in our SE channel and <#CV8V33RPV|> while asking a product question. @Eric Han encouraged me sharing this a little wider, so hopefully this brings a... smile? astonished look? to your faces on this Thursday morning!

This is the Bank of America :bofa: _Home Loan Navigator_ development flow. Mega-classifier for 400+ doc types (currently 35 in prod) and sub-classifiers for business vs personal banking statements, 401k vs IRA statements, etc. Some of the BAC folks and I were joking that they can't actually screen share the flow with some team members because their monitors won't support it! Happy Thursday :slightly_smiling_face:
how can we get this as a test Flow? :eyes:
Results files would benefit from a Flow mini-map for Flows like this.
